{
  "title":"Should",
  "date":"2010-07-11 CST",
  "origin":"Funny Logic",
  "url":"text-should",
  "author":"Ryan X. Charles"
}


<p>&#8220;Things should be better,&#8221; she said.</p>

<p>
&#8220;Indeed,&#8221; he said.
&#8220;The grass should be greener and the sky should be bluer.
Maybe if we keep saying out loud how things should be better, they will become better.
Things should be better.
Things should be better.
Things should be worse.
Fuck, I mean better.&#8221;</p>

<p>He had to stop talking then because he had fulfilled his sarcasm quota for the day.</p>

